Fergussen, my Master bids you to come more often, something about the taste of pine needles and forest dew... can't see it though, I perfer much more the blood brewed in Felwithe.  Alas, Hate.  Interesting, for once I'm filled with an uncomfortable feeling that I could attribute to the dread I see in my victims eyes... not a place for a quiet &quot;picnic&quot; that Centuri always spoke of...<br>
